metrics forbidding the existence of any timelike CO.
However, these metrics are not asymptotically flat. People are
usually more interested in asymptotically flat spacetimes
due to their physical relevance. Therefore in this section
we analyze how the asymptotic flatness condition will
affect the existences of timelike COs in the SAS spacetimes.</p>
