    <sec id="sec-10">
      <title>Appendix B: Proof of Theorem F</title>
      <p>To prove the theorem, we define a µ (ρ) first
such that</p>
      <p>µ (ρ) = A(ρ)/ρ
µ ′(ρ) = [A′(ρ)ρ − A(ρ)] /ρ2.
